high_descs: Turn to the right and walk to the bin to the right of the refrigerator.
Grab the potato out of the bin.
Turn to the right and walk to the microwave.
Place the potato onto the plate in the microwave.
Close the microwave, turn right and walk to the sink.
Pick up the potato that is beside the tomato on the counter to the left of the sink.
Turn to the left and walk to the microwave.
Open the microwave and place the potato on the plate with the other potato and close the door.
Turn to your right and go to the trash can next to the fridge.
Grab the potato out of the trash can
Go to your right and up to the microwave
Put the potato in the microwave, on the plate
Turn to your right and go to the sink
Pick up the potato in front of you
Turn back around and go back to the microwave
Put the potato on the left of the previous potato
anns.task_desc: Grab two potatoes, placing both into a microwave

high_descs: Turn right and walk over to the small silver trashcan between the fridge and kitchen counter.
Pick up the potato that is in the small silver trashcan.
Turn around and walk forward, then turn left and walk over to the microwave.
Open the microwave and place the potato inside to the left of the glass, then close the microwave.
Turn around and take a step forward, then turn left and walk over to the kitchen sink.
Pick up the potato to the left of the kitchen sink.
Turn around and walk back to the microwave.
Open the microwave and place the second potato inside to the left of the potato that is already in there, then close the microwave door.
anns.task_desc: Move two potatoes into the microwave.
